Work records and salary calculator

Application for recording working hours and calculating their salaries.
The program should enable:
• adding employees (first name, last name, time rate),
• recording the hours worked for each employee on a given day,
• editing and deleting entries.
The program should calculate:
• monthly salary based on hours worked and rate,
• overtime allowance (e.g., over 160 hours – +50% rate),
• total shutdown costs for the entire company.
The program should have the following data viewing capabilities:
• a list of all employees and their hours worked,
• filtering by month or assigned employee.
The data can be used in a file (e.g., txt).
Exception handling for incorrect data.
